{"tid":1385544,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"外國記者 Nury Vittachi 暴徒戇鳩個 post del 咗","createTime":"2019-07-30T06:02:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T07:18:00.000Z","uid":279063,"like":45,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"08049140bf14fd66dd783a250e2301e8e695db63","tid":1385544,"uid":279063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T06:02:05.000Z","msg":"琴日po 咗出佢笑我地叫人 del 相唔識 del backup嘅 post 上嚟，上咗熱門，好多英文文宣組入去留言，<span style=\"color: red;\">唔到一個鐘佢已經驚到del 咗個 post </span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n外國記者 Nury Vittachi 笑你班暴徒戇鳩<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1380739\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1380739</a><br />\n<br />\n(好多巴絲提返大家其實出去發夢都係 black bloc 保護自己好啲，其實我地無權叫記者 del 相㗎。)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>佢啱啱終於出新 post 啦</strong></span><br />\n話 FB 係同溫層溫床，叫你唔好因為政見不同 unfriend 人。係講得啱，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">但係之前個 post 一有反對聲音，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">佢就 del 咗</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BXvi8yE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBXvi8yE.jpg&h=005794fa&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢之前剪咗成條片話和你飛會嚇親遊客，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">叫你班示威者和平啲，唔好嗌口號嚇親人喎，仲話叫叫下可能政府會出老解</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t9ULOAo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft9ULOAo.jpg&h=f188300b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Gz1yc2J.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGz1yc2J.jpg&h=79c86c54&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vBH5OA3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvBH5OA3.jpg&h=588a516c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一有反對聲音就 del post, 咁大家入去留多啲言，佢啲  post 咪要全部 del 